<法規>
<法規性質>命令</法規性質>
<英文法規名稱>Sanitation Standard for Pork Fat</英文法規名稱>
<中文法規名稱>食用豬脂衛生標準</中文法規名稱>
<法規網址>http://law.moj.gov.tw/Eng/LawClass/LawContent.aspx?PCODE=L0040129</法規網址>
<最新英文異動日期>20150716</最新英文異動日期>
<廢止註記>
</廢止註記>
<沿革內容><![CDATA[1.MOHW Food No. 1041301568 promulgated, July 16, 2015.]]></沿革內容>
<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This Standard is prescribed in accordance with the provisions of Article 17 of the Act Governing Food Safety and Sanitation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The raw materials of pork fat shall meet the “Act Governing Food Safety and Sanitation”, obtaining from swine fatty tissues in good health, clean and fit for human consumption. The tissues for raw materials do not include viscera, brains, spinal marrow and large blood vessels.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Pork fat shall have good color, no off odor or flat-sour spoilage flavor.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Pork fat shall have acid value not more than 2.0 mg KOH/g fat. The refined pork fats, which have the process for refining, bleaching and deodorization, shall have acid value not more than 1.3 mg KOH/g fat. Both of them shall be in accordance with the other relevant standards set from the “Act Governing Food Safety and Sanitation”.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 5</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This standard shall be implemented from the date of promulgation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
</法規>
